Question: Each image contains one tablet-type device, and one image shows the device with the screen inverted.

Reference Answer: True

Left image URL: https://www.kv.by/sites/default/files/user535/asus_taichi_31.jpg

Right image URL: http://insmart.cz/wp-content/uploads/2017/05/hp-laptop.jpg

Program:

```
ANSWER0=VQA(image=LEFT,question='Does the image show a tablet-type device?')
ANSWER1=VQA(image=RIGHT,question='Does the image show a tablet-type device?')
ANSWER2=VQA(image=LEFT,question='Is the screen inverted?')
ANSWER3=VQA(image=RIGHT,question='Is the screen inverted?')
ANSWER4=EVAL(expr='{ANSWER0} and {ANSWER2}')
ANSWER5=EVAL(expr='{ANSWER1} and {ANSWER3}')
ANSWER6=EVAL(expr='{ANSWER4} xor {ANSWER5}')
FINAL_ANSWER=RESULT(var=ANSWER6)
```
